Dataset all about meteorites, where they fell and when they fell! Data comes from the Meteoritical Society by way of NASA

Parsed with column specification:
cols(
  name = col_character(),
  id = col_double(),
  name_type = col_character(),
  class = col_character(),
  mass = col_double(),
  fall = col_character(),
  year = col_double(),
  lat = col_double(),
  long = col_double(),
  geolocation = col_character()
)
